edu.brown.cs.cdluo.stars

Class DumbTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.cdluo.stars.DumbTree

  • public class DumbTree
extends Object
    A Dumb version of my KDTree. It has all the same methods, but for KNN and radius search, it just does a BFS to get the answer.
    Author:
    cdluo
